OL,3,CEngland Rugby boss defends bonus and
OL,4,Cresists calls to resign
OL,6,FThe head of the RFU defended his
OL,7,Fdecision not to step down, telling ITV
OL,8,FNews that he would consider quitting
OL,9,Fto be an 'easy option'
OL,11,FAdditional words by Joe Wardropper,
OL,12,FITV News Senior Producer
OL,14,FBill Sweeney, the RFU chief executive
OL,15,Ffacing a grassroots rebellion over his
OL,16,Fbonus, has told ITV News he has not
OL,17,Fconsidered resigning over the crisis.
