OL,6,F"I fully understand the upset and the
OL,7,Fangst about what's gone on since the
OL,8,Fpublication of the annual report," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"But at no stage did I think about
OL,12,Fstepping down, I think to step down
OL,13,Fnow would simply be taking an easy
OL,14,Foption."
OL,16,FIt was revealed in November that
OL,17,FSweeney was paid #1.1m for the 2023-24
OL,18,Ffinancial year, including a bonus
OL,19,Fworth #358,000, despite the RFU making
OL,20,Frecord losses and laying off dozens of
OL,21,Fstaff.
