OL,6,F"It doesn't look good at all, you
OL,7,Fknow, and I could see that coming," he
OL,8,Fsaid, reiterating that he'd have
OL,9,Fpreferred to see the bonus deferred.
OL,11,FHis critics have suggested he hand
OL,12,Fback the bonus or donate it to charity.
OL,14,FSweeney said he didn't believe that
OL,15,Fwas "necessary".
OL,17,F"It was a scheme that was put in place
OL,18,Fby the board to achieve certain
OL,19,Ftargets," he said.
