OL,6,F"The targets are very clear, and the
OL,7,Fmeans of measuring it were very clear.
OL,8,FAnd that bonus has been earned by
OL,9,Fmyself and the executive team."
OL,11,FSweeney defended his management of the
OL,12,FRFU's finances, pointing to #100m of
OL,13,Finvestment in the game over the four-
OL,14,Fyear international cycle. He has also
OL,15,Fhighlighted that the union now has
OL,16,Fzero debt, #59m in cash and #80m of
OL,17,Freserves.
