OL,6,FThe beleaguered CEO also told ITV News
OL,7,Fhe'd met senior England players to
OL,8,Fdiscuss the crisis, saying: "I haven't
OL,9,Fspoken to every single member, but
OL,10,Fyou've got a group of core players...
OL,11,FI've explained the situation, I've
OL,12,Fexplained my own personal salary
OL,13,Fstructure, I've explained how it
OL,14,Fcompares to other sports, and I've
OL,15,Fexplained how it compares to the
OL,16,Fprevious, CEOs, here in the RFU."
