OL,6,FSweeney will now face a special
OL,7,Fgeneral meeting on March 27, after the
OL,8,FSix Nations, where clubs could table a
OL,9,Fno-confidence vote, but before then he
OL,10,Fwill embark on a listening tour of
OL,11,Fgrassroots teams across the country.
OL,13,FMore than 150 clubs have already
OL,14,Fcalled on Sweeney to quit, citing
OL,15,Fgovernance concerns, a lack of funding
OL,16,Ffor the amateur game, the bungled roll
OL,17,Fout of new tackle height rules in 2023
OL,18,Fand the "wasted money spent on sacking
OL,19,FEngland coaching staff", as well as
OL,20,Fthe bonus row.
