OL,6,FRob Sigley, the founder of Community
OL,7,FClubs Union, told ITV News told: "This
OL,8,Fyear alone we've had 400 games
OL,9,Fcancelled because there's not enough
OL,10,Fplayers to fulfil the fixtures, we've
OL,11,Fgot in excess of 20 teams falling out
OL,12,Fof the league system because we can't
OL,13,Fget the teams together, and on top of
OL,14,Fthat some of the games are cancelled
OL,15,Fbecause there's not enough match
OL,16,Fofficials.
